\theta
\theta=90^\circ
(a,b)
 x=acos(t)cos(\theta)+bsin(t)sin(\theta) 
t
 \frac{dx}{dt}=-asin(t)cos(\theta)+bcos(t)sin(\theta)=0 
 asin(t)cos(\theta)=bcos(t)sin(\theta) 
 tan(t)=\frac{b}{a}tan(\theta) 
