t
y
 y=-acos(t)sin(\theta) + bsin(t)cos(\theta) 
 \frac{dy}{dt}=asin(t)sin(\theta)+bcos(t)cos(\theta)=0 
 asin(t)sin(\theta)=-bcos(t)cos(\theta) 
 tan(t)=-\frac{b}{a}cot(\theta) 
